code: export var taskCleaner=function taskCleaner(tasks,orders,projects){var result=[];if(!tasks){return;}for(var i=0;i<tasks.length;i++){if(tasks[i].ProjectNo){if(Object.keys(projects).includes(tasks[i].ProjectNo)){result.push(tasks[i]);continue;}}if(tasks[i].OrderNo){if(Object.keys(orders).includes(tasks[i].OrderNo)){result.push(tasks[i]);continue;}}}return result;};
